                                                                                            "text":  "Hardcoded cryptographic key in .NET config appSettings (+1 more affected)"
                                                                                        },
                                                                   "fullDescription":  {
                                                                                           "text":  "Never ship a symmetric or private key in config. Derive a per-user key (DPAPI) or fetch from a key vault; rotate the exposed key. With key+IV+ciphertext all present, the protected value is trivially decryptable."
